                    <h2>üìå Note colors</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="p-1">
                        You can use <code class="text-bold text-primary">btn-{color}</code> if you want a hover effect.
                        If you do not need hover, use <code class="text-bold text-primary">bg-{color}</code> or your own
                        custom class.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </article>

            {# Note about state #}
            <article class="card p-2">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h2>üìå Note open state</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="p-1">
                        To keep a panel open on page load, add the <code class="text-bold text-primary">.show</code>
                        class on the
                        <code class="text-bold text-primary">.accordion-body</code>. The panel opens automatically and
                        the button shows <strong>Ôπ£</strong>.
